'''查爾斯·蘭道夫'''（Charles Randolph）是一名[[美国|美国]][[编剧|编剧]]和影视监制。他编剧的主要作品有 ''The Life of David Gale'' (2003), 《[[翻译风波|翻译风波]]》(2005)和《[[爱情与灵药|爱情与灵药]]》(2010)。2015年联合编剧的电影《[[大空头|大空头]]》为他赢得[[奥斯卡奖|奥斯卡奖]]和[[英国电影学院奖|英国电影学院奖]]最佳改编剧本奖<ref>{{cite web|title=Oscar Winners 2016|url=http://oscar.go.com/news/winners/oscar-winners-2016-see-the-complete-list|accessdate=29 February 2016|archive-date=2016-03-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160301232004/http://oscar.go.com/news/winners/oscar-winners-2016-see-the-complete-list|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 简介 ==
他生于田纳西州[[纳什维尔|纳什维尔]]，是一名[[文化研究|文化研究]]<ref name=IF>{{cite web|last1=Gavin|first1=Rachael|title=Love and Other Drugs screenwriter Charles Randolph on big screen opportunities|url=http://if.com.au/2012/01/17/article/Love-and-Other-Drugs-screenwriter-Charles-Randolph-on-big-screen-opportunities/DSOMVGKXXZ.html|website=if.com.au|accessdate=18 December 2015|date=18 January 2012|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304061016/http://if.com.au/2012/01/17/article/Love-and-Other-Drugs-screenwriter-Charles-Randolph-on-big-screen-opportunities/DSOMVGKXXZ.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>和[[哲学|哲学]]教授。<ref name=IMDb>{{cite web|title=Charles Randolph –Biography|url=http://www.imdb.com/name/nm1017488/bio?ref_=nm_ov_bio_sm#trivia|website=[[IMDb|IMDb]]|accessdate=18 December 2015|archive-date=2021-07-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210702162628/https://www.imdb.com/name/nm1017488/bio?ref_=nm_ov_bio_sm#trivia|dead-url=no}}</ref>他妻子是[[以色列|以色列]]女演员[[Mili_Avital|Mili Avital]]，两人育有2个孩子。

